# CRM Field Agent — Design System Rules
# Place this file at: .cursor/rules/design-system.mdc
# Cursor AI will automatically inject this context when generating UI code.

## Design System Overview

This project uses a **Salesforce FSL-equivalent design system** targeting zero friction for existing Salesforce users.
All styling is done via:
1. CSS custom properties defined in `src/styles/tokens.css`
2. Tailwind utility classes extended in `tailwind.config.js` under the `sf-*` namespace
3. Pre-built component classes in `src/styles/globals.css` under `@layer components`

---

## Critical Rules

- **NEVER hardcode hex colors.** Always use `var(--sf-*)` CSS variables or `sf-*` Tailwind classes.
- **NEVER use arbitrary Tailwind values** like `bg-[#4BCA81]`. Use `bg-sf-success` instead.
- **ALWAYS use `font-sf` class** on top-level layout components to ensure SF font stack.
- **Status colors are semantic** — use the named token, not the shade (e.g. `bg-sf-success-bg`, not `bg-green-100`).
- **Spacing follows the 4px grid** — use `sf-*` spacing tokens, not arbitrary `p-3`, `m-5` etc.

---

## Token Quick Reference

### Shell & Brand
| Token | Tailwind Class | Use |
|-------|---------------|-----|
| `var(--sf-navy)` | `bg-sf-navy` | App header background |
| `var(--sf-brand)` | `bg-sf-brand` / `text-sf-brand` | Primary buttons, links, active states |
| `var(--sf-brand-light)` | `bg-sf-brand-light` | Selected rows, info highlight |
| `var(--sf-bg-page)` | `bg-sf-bg-page` | Page background, Gantt grid |
| `var(--sf-bg-surface)` | `bg-sf-bg-surface` | Cards, panels, list area |
| `var(--sf-border)` | `border-sf-border` | All dividers |

### Text
| Token | Tailwind Class | Use |
|-------|---------------|-----|
| `var(--sf-text-primary)` | `text-sf-text-primary` | Main labels, record names |
| `var(--sf-text-secondary)` | `text-sf-text-secondary` | Column headers, field labels |
| `var(--sf-text-muted)` | `text-sf-text-muted` | Zone, frequency, hints |
| `var(--sf-text-inverse)` | `text-sf-text-inverse` | Text on dark/navy backgrounds |

### Status
| State | Background | Text | Border |
|-------|-----------|------|--------|
| Success / Completed | `bg-sf-success-bg` | `text-sf-success-dark` | `border-sf-success` |
| Warning | `bg-sf-warning-bg` | `text-[var(--sf-warning-text)]` | `border-sf-warning-strong` |
| Error | `bg-sf-error-bg` | `text-[var(--sf-error-text)]` | `border-sf-error` |
| Info / Selected | `bg-sf-info-bg` | `text-sf-navy` | `border-sf-info` |

### Gantt Blocks
| Block Type | Class |
|------------|-------|
| Scheduled appointment | `sf-gantt-block-scheduled` |
| Travel / drive time | `sf-gantt-block-travel` |
| Constraint violation | `sf-gantt-block-violation` |

